msgstr "Skærmaftryk af &kiten;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Dictionary"
msgstr "Brug af ordbogen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kiten;'s most basic mode is as a dictionary for looking up both English and "
"Japanese words. You can also add other dictionaries to &kiten;'s list."
msgstr ""
"&kiten;'s mest basale funktion er som en ordbog til at slå både engelske og "
"japanske ord op. Du kan også  tilføje andre ordbøger til &kiten;'s liste."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:80
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. "
#| "You can find more information at <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu."
#| "au/~jwb/edict.html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"http://"
#| "www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic.html\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgid ""
"&kiten; uses Jim Breen's Edict and Kanjidic as the default dictionaries. You "
"can find more information at <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/jmdict/edict."
"html\">the Edict web site</ulink> and <ulink url=\"https://www.edrdg.org/"
"wiki/index.php/KANJIDIC_Project\">the Kanjidic web site</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&kiten; bruger Jim Breen's Edict og Kanjidic som standardordbøger. Du kan "
"finde mere information på <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash.edu.au/~jwb/"
"edict.html\">Edict's net-sted</ulink> og <ulink url=\"http://www.csse.monash."
"edu.au/~jwb/kanjidic.html\">Kanjidic net-stedet</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "Looking Up Words"
msgstr "Opslag af ord"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
#| "like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either <keycap>Enter</keycap> "
#| "or the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> button on the toolbar (again, much "
#| "like &konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgid ""
"To look up words in either language, type them in to the text-edit (much "
"like &konqueror;'s location bar) and press either &Enter; or the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button on the toolbar (again, much like "
"&konqueror;). &kiten; will then look up the word."
msgstr ""
"For at slå ord op på et af sprogene, skrives de i tekst-editoren (meget "
"ligesom &konqueror;'s stedlinje) og der trykkes enten på <keycap>Enter</"
"keycap> eller  <guilabel>Søg</guilabel>-knappen i værktøjslinjen (igen, "
"meget ligesom &konqueror;). &kiten; vil så slå ordet op."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enter Kanji, Kana and English and get back results from &kiten;. "
"These results of your search will appear in the large results view which "
"takes up the majority of the &kiten; window."
msgstr ""
"Du kan indtaste kanji, kana og engelsk og få resultater tilbage fra &kiten;. "
"Disse resultater af din  søgning vil vise sig i den store resultatvisning "
"som optager størstedelen af &kiten;-vinduet."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "searching for an English translation"
msgstr "søger efter en engelsk oversættelse"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kiten; search screenshot"
msgstr "&kiten; søgning-skærmaftryk"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filtering"
msgstr "Filtrering"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:106
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Often times you will want to filter rare words from your search. &kiten; "
#| "will do this for you if toggle <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
#| "guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Rare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgid ""
"Often times you will want to filter rare words from your search. &kiten; "
"will do this for you if toggle <menuchoice><guimenu>Search</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filter Out Rare</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Ofte vil du ønske at filtrere sjældne ord væk fra din søgning. &kiten; vil "
"gøre dette for dig hvis du skifter med <menuchoice><guimenu>Opsætning</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Filtrér sjældne</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Not all dictionary files support filtering rare entries - most dictionaries, "
"excluding the two provided by default in &kiten; do not."
msgstr ""
"Ikke alle ordbøger understøtter filtrering af sjældne indgange - de fleste "
"ordbøger gør ikke, bortset fra de to der som standard kommer med &kiten;."

