#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:386
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&Qt; 3's new font-substitution system makes it so a Japanese font will "
#| "always be substituted for Japanese characters, even if the font you "
#| "specify doesn't include them. Thus, you can choose any font in the "
#| "chooser and everything should still display fine."
msgid ""
"&Qt; 's font-substitution system makes it so a Japanese font will always be "
"substituted for Japanese characters, even if the font you specify doesn't "
"include them. Thus, you can choose any font in the chooser and everything "
"should still display fine."
msgstr ""
"&Qt; 3's nye skrifttype-substitutionssystem gør det sådan at en japansk "
"skrifttype altid vil blive substitueret for japanske tegn, også selvom "
"skrifttypen du angiver  ikke inkluderer dem. Således kan du vælge en "
"vilkårlig skrifttype i vælgeren og det hele skulle stadig blive vist fint."

